profile_summary:
V Vignesh Iyer is a skilled software developer with expertise in data science and software engineering. With a strong academic foundation from the National Institute of Technology, Trichy, class of '21, Vignesh has honed his skills in Jupyter Notebook, Python, and Java to deliver high-quality solutions. His experience in leveraging these technologies enables him to drive innovative projects forward.

Vignesh boasts an impressive professional network, with 55 members recognizing his expertise, and maintains an active portfolio of 18 public repositories, showcasing his experience in collaborative development and continuous learning. Having worked with organizations like Capgemini, Vignesh brings industry-relevant experience, ensuring seamless collaboration and dependable technical expertise to tackle complex projects. With his unique blend of analytical skills, technical proficiency, and passion for innovation, Vignesh is positioned to drive business value and optimize software development.
